modules.description: This module implements HTTP/HTTPS client operations for interacting with Git services using the Paf framework. It provides `get` and `post` functions to send requests with custom headers and handle responses asynchronously, returning result values with unit and body or error types. The module works directly with `Uri.t`, `Mimic.ctx`, and string payloads, targeting concrete use cases like fetching and pushing Git data over HTTP(S) in networked applications.
